raining experience shows leadership potential. However, lacks specific quantifiable achievements and installation experience details.', 70, NULL, '["Add specific technical accomplishments","Include measurable results","Add education section","Expand job descriptions with more detail","Include safety record"]', 'Well-organized but somewhat brief. Good use of metrics where included, but needs more specific examples of technical achievements and problem-solving results.', '["Strong diagnostic and troubleshooting capabilities","Excellent customer service record (4.9-star rating)","Essential HVAC certifications (EPA 608 Universal, NATE)","Training and mentoring experience","High service call volume with proven track record"]', '["Limited evidence of installation experience","Missing gas heating and commercial system experience","No safety training or protocols mentioned","Lacks specific technical achievements or problem-solving examples","No manufacturer-specific certifications or training"]', '["Add quantifiable technical achievements (e.g., ''Improved first-time fix rate by X%'')","Pursue additional NATE certifications in Heat Pump and Gas Furnace","Include specific examples of complex problems solved","Add safety training certifications (OSHA 10/30)","Expand experience descriptions to include installation and preventive maintenance work"]', 'YES', '2025-10-04 21:02:25', '2025-10-04 21:02:25') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
