e work"]', 'Excellent progression from tech to lead installer with impressive project volume. However, experience is heavily skewed toward installation with no evident service/maintenance background.', 75, NULL, '["Add education section","Include more technical details","Expand skill descriptions","Add customer service examples","Include safety record/metrics"]', 'Well-structured and concise but could benefit from more technical depth and broader skill demonstration. Missing education background entirely.', '["6+ years progressive HVAC experience with leadership responsibility","High project volume (100+) demonstrates productivity and reliability","Commercial experience with complex RTU systems","Team leadership and apprentice training capabilities","Essential EPA and safety certifications in place"]', '["Limited to installation work - no service, repair, or maintenance experience shown","Missing EPA 608 Universal certification limits system types he can work on","No NATE certifications which are industry standard","Lacks troubleshooting and diagnostic skills critical for technician roles","No evidence of customer service experience or soft skills"]', '["Pursue EPA 608 Universal certification to work on all refrigeration systems","Obtain NATE Installation and Service certifications to validate skills","Gain service/maintenance experience to become a well-rounded technician","Add education section including trade school, apprenticeship, or relevant training","Include examples of problem-solving, customer interaction, and safety achievements"]', 'YES', '2025-10-04 21:02:43', '2025-10-04 21:02:43') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
