e with commercial chillers and building automation systems","Obtain manufacturer certifications from major equipment brands","Develop load calculation and blueprint reading skills through continuing education"]', 'YES', '2025-10-04 21:04:03', '2025-10-04 21:04:03') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
