f Texas","ServiceTitan Administrator"]', '["HVAC dispatcher certification","Customer service certification"]', 'The candidate has some relevant certifications, such as being a Notary and a ServiceTitan Administrator, which demonstrate their administrative and technical skills. However, they could benefit from pursuing additional certifications specifically related to HVAC dispatch and customer service to further strengthen their qualifications for this role.', 85, 6, '["General Manager of Operations overseeing daily operations, developing strategic plans, and improving revenue generation","HVAC Install Coordinator responsible for monitoring and tracking progress of installations, troubleshooting issues, and ensuring compliance with safety regulations","New Construction Coordinator managing scheduling, training, and inventory control","Operations Manager coordinating installation activities with customers, communicating with distributors, and reviewing customer feedback"]', 'The candidate has a strong background in operations management, customer service, and project coordination, which are highly relevant to the HVAC Dispatcher role. Their experience in overseeing daily operations, implementing process improvements, and delivering positive customer experiences demonstrates the necessary skills for this position. The combination of their diverse experience and years of relevant work history make them a strong candidate for the HVAC Dispatcher role.', 90, '["Clear and concise resume formatting","Detailed and well-structured work experience descriptions","Consistent use of professional language and tone"]', '["Could include a more focused summary statement tailored to the HVAC Dispatcher role"]', 'The candidate''s resume is well-presented, with a clear and organized structure, professional language, and detailed work experience descriptions. The overall quality of the resume is high, making it easy for the reader to understand the candidate''s qualifications and experience. A more targeted summary statement focused on the HVAC Dispatcher role would further strengthen the resume.', '["Strong operations management experience","Excellent customer service and communication skills","Proven ability to implement process improvements and increase efficiency","Experienced in managing teams and coordinating cross-functional projects","Proficient in using various software and technologies"]', '["Lacks specific experience with HVAC dispatch software and equipment knowledge","Could benefit from additional certifications or training related to HVAC dispatch and customer service"]', '["Pursue HVAC dispatcher certification or training to gain specialized knowledge and skills","Obtain a customer service certification to further demonstrate their commitment to delivering exceptional customer experiences","Highlight any relevant HVAC equipment knowledge or experience in their resume or cover letter","Consider taking on a temporary or contract HVAC dispatcher role to gain hands-on experience in the field"]', 'STRONG_YES', '2025-11-19 23:41:42', '2025-11-19 23:41:42') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
