an HVAC Dispatcher Certification and a Customer Service Certification would further strengthen her qualifications and demonstrate her commitment to the industry and role.', 90, 8, '["HVAC and Plumbing Dispatcher","Permit Coordinator","Customer Service Representative","Scheduling and dispatching for new construction and warranty crews"]', 'Dianne has an impressive 8 years of relevant experience in the HVAC, plumbing, and construction industries, with a strong focus on dispatch, customer service, and coordination roles. Her diverse background in these areas makes her well-suited for the HVAC Dispatcher position.', 85, '["Clear and organized resume format","Consistent use of professional language and tone","Detailed descriptions of job responsibilities"]', '["Could include a brief summary or objective statement at the top of the resume"]', 'Dianne''s resume is well-presented, with a clear and organized format, professional language, and detailed job descriptions. Adding a brief summary or objective statement at the top would further strengthen the overall presentation.', '["Extensive experience in HVAC and plumbing dispatch roles","Proven track record of providing excellent customer service","Skilled in scheduling, permit coordination, and report generation","Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite","Ability to communicate effectively with various stakeholders"]', '["Lack of formal HVAC Dispatcher certification","Limited experience with specialized HVAC dispatch software"]', '["Obtain an HVAC Dispatcher Certification to demonstrate industry-specific expertise","Gain experience or training with HVAC dispatch software (e.g., ServiceTitan, FieldEdge)","Consider adding a brief summary or objective statement at the top of the resume"]', 'STRONG_YES', '2025-11-19 23:41:49', '2025-11-19 23:41:49') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
