ey technical strengths rather than medical/IT background","Include quantifiable achievements (e.g., ''Maintained 95% first-call resolution rate'' or ''Serviced 200+ residential units annually'')","Consider consolidating overlapping positions or explaining the business model (e.g., contractor working for multiple companies)","Pursue manufacturer-specific certifications to demonstrate ongoing professional development and specialization"]', 'MAYBE (50-79)', '2025-11-20 00:21:19', '2025-11-20 00:21:19') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
