ncrease marketability","Add quantifiable achievements to resume (e.g., ''Maintained 98% first-call resolution rate'' or ''Serviced 200+ units annually'')","Consider obtaining manufacturer certifications from major brands (Carrier, Trane, Lennox) to complement Data Aire expertise","Streamline non-HVAC work history to 2-3 bullets to keep focus on HVAC accomplishments","Add a brief explanation in cover letter about transition from self-employment to manufacturer role to address potential questions"]', 'STRONG_YES (90-100)', '2025-11-20 00:21:59', '2025-11-20 00:21:59') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
